text: Vasilios Ganotis (born 16 February 1942) is a Greek wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics, the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Greek male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Greece Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics
